            "title": "Learning Without School : Home Education",
            "abstract": [
                "This book explains what home education is; the advantages and disadvantages of this route; how to begin home educating; what you need to do and how to help your child adjust; and how home education affects children&apos;s social skills and friendships. It also covers technical aspects, such as the curriculum, core subjects, exams and timetables.",
